      About this item

      • Remote Battery Disconnect Switch Function: Long term parking, electronic device power consumption, line aging, forgetting to turn off the lights, which will cause battery to run out and vehicle cannot start normally, installing our kill switch can maximize the storage of car battery power, effectively protecting and extending lifespan
      • Remote control distance 30-70M, rated voltage 12V, rated current 120A,500A Cranking Current, instantaneous current 2400A, battery disconnect switch is suitable for cars, boats, campers, RVs, ships, travel trailers, beaches with displacement less than 4.0 Cars, motorcycles, etc
      • Smart Voltage Kill Switch: battery kill switch detects the voltage at all times. In smart mode, when the battery voltage is lower than 11.9V, the switch will automatically turn off after 5 minutes, when the battery voltage is higher than 13.3V(for example, driving), remote will not control the switch
      • The standby current of this car kill switch anti theft is only 0.005A, which is far lower than the standby current of the original car, which is more than 65 mA. It will not drain your battery
      • The car battery switch is made of pure copper. Durable and reliable. The battery disconnect isolator is upgraded from the old model, because the improved accessories make the installation contact more secure.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
